Beginning at the two-story foyer, a grand staircase leads to a catwalk above that overlooks the river through a wall of windows in the two-story great room and its massive, floor-to-ceiling, stone surround gas fireplace.  Open to the great room is an informal dining area, wonderfully surrounded by windows and patio doors that lead to a large, maintenance-free deck outside, also conveniently located near the kitchen.  Adorned with gorgeous cherry cabinetry and light Corian countertops, you will enjoy desired kitchen amenities, such as an additional prep sink, walk-in pantry and raised countertop seating. A set of glass French doors leads to the master suite that feels like a sanctuary with its vaulted ceiling and breathtaking river views, and its beautiful bath is the perfect place to unwind in its oversized shower or soaking tub.
